[00:50.37] Mou neru ze ashita kara mata baito da
[01:08.87] 
[00:55.58] Netsukezu ni ore ha manga wo mekutta
[01:00.53] Gurabia no aidoru hohoendeita
[01:05.73] (asuriito ga watashi no taipu nano yo.
