[01:30.58] 
[01:16.27] Wakatta ze mukuwarenu sono wake
[01:21.42] Hito toshite ore, jiku ga buretenda
[01:38.92] 
[01:25.17] Sore naraba inaore! Mou
[01:28.72] Bure-bure-bure-bure-bure magutte
[01:31.96] Furueteru no wakannee you nishite yare!
